    dc:description "FIGURE 33. Female galea setae. Scale=0.5 mm. A) Typical, negligible at most, usually absent (A. curta, KWC0014764). B) Long, curved toward tip (A. caudata, BBSLID99042). C) Long, apically bent (A. erythrothorax, UCRCENT335468). D) Long, mop-like (A. abroniae, BBSL920101)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3771049/files/figure.png" ;
